data.description: Welcome home, this is the one you have been waiting for! It checks all of the boxes on your list & seller will entertain closing costs! 4 bedrooms 2.5 baths situated on a spacious lot with off-street access road entry to home. Family room with wet bar, modern kitchen with soft close cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, & more. Large primary bedroom with ensuite along with double bowl vanities, tile flooring, dual showers, & custom walk-in closet. Relax, relate, or release while enjoying the screened porch with a private fenced-in backyard. Close to interstates, beaches, shopping, bases, & more, don't let this one slip away; schedule appt. today!
